title: 'Takes care of lot of things required for storage.'
body: 'I have been using these boxes to store clothes for almost 4 months now. The are very useful because:- 1. The boxes are incredibly sturdy and can you can stuff them up to full capacity without any fear for structural integrity. 2. Very easy to assemble and disassemble. 3. Can be stowed on top of each other. No worries about sagging or pressure on lower boxes. 4. Saves a lot of space especially if you want to store clothes.'

title: 'File Storage'
body: 'I plan to use these cardboard boxes to store files. They came in 2 parts: lid and box. The parts are flat to facilitate packaging -- 5 boxes per package. But the fold lines are clear and I assembled each box in a few minutes. The boxes can be used to store documents from letter to legal size.'
